Body: U.CASH • Cash Meets Digital Currencies •  U.CASH is a peer to peer, financial service platform designed for the entire world. Go seamlessly between digital currencies and fiat cash through our retail converter network. Access financial services on the U.CASH platform.  WHITEPAPER  WEBSITE  TELEGRAM  TWITTER  FACEBOOK  REDDIT  TO FIND OUT MORE ABOUT OUR PROJECT PLEASE VISIT OUR ANN THREAD & WEBSITE   HELLO EVERYONE WHO HAS BEEN FOLLOWING ALONG AND THOSE WHO ARE NEW! OUR IBO IS NOW COMPLETE AND WE HAVE EACHED 100% OF OUR GOAL OF 8,494,678,440.00 UCASH DISTRIBUTED (>113M USD). PLEASE VISIT OUR WEBSITE TO STAY UP TO DATE WITH NEW ANNOUNCEMENTS.  OUR MISSION: Free your money.  U.CASH opens the world up to massive fintech innovation by giving the world access to a distributed cash network.  More than 2 billion people have no access to traditional financial services. One of our primary goals is providing financial inclusion while also bridging the gap between cash and cryptocurrencies in developed and developing nations. Anyone with a computing device and internet connection will be able to access the U.CASH platform, gaining access to essential financial services.    WHAT IS UCASH:  U.CASH is unbanking the world! U.CASH is a global peer to peer platform designed designed for everyone.  By utilizing our platform and a global network of online and live converters, users and converters will be able to instantly deposit or withdraw from their U.CASH accounts using cash or digital assets alike. Once on the platform, users and converters across the globe gain access to a full gauntlet of decentralized financial and blockchain services:  Foreign and Crypto Exchange: Instantly convert your balance to local currencies and crypto assets. Secure remittance: Send your money and assets instantly anywhere around the world Pay your bills Spend your cash anywhere: Virtual NFC credit cards and Physical Debit Cards Credit: access to loans and credit services Value storing:Store of value and value locking And more… imagine the possibilities   The U.CASH Currency  UCASH will initially be an ERC20 token.  Total Supply of UCASH: 21,000,000,000 Decimals in UCASH: 17 Symbol: UCASH  UCASH is the fuel of the U.CASH network. UCASH is a universal access key which grants users access to services and advanced functionality on the U.CASH network. Using the network allows users to transact with any currency or asset they like. U.CASH is designed to be blockchain agnostic so we can adapt with any industry changes.  Join the IBO - Earn UCASH IBO means Initial Bounty Offering. The Majority of network access tokens are distributed to those who complete U.CASH bounties. Bounty hunters help us grow our network by performing valuable tasks.  No need to invest, you can work for your UCASH!  Participate in the IBO now and earn UCASH!  START: SEPTEMBER 8TH 2017 END: JANUARY 7TH 2018  LIVE BOUNTIES  Sign up for an account: 500 UCASH *** Verify yourself for an additional 1000 UCASH Translate the white paper : UP TO 500,000.00 UCASH Translate the website : UP TO 100,000.00 UCASH Create a video: UP TO 300,000.00 UCASH Write a news source article : UP TO 200,000.00 UCASH Reddit Post with 25 upvotes: UP TO 50,000.00 UCASH Medium Blog post: UP TO 50,000 UCASH Steemit post: UP TO 50,000 UCASH Industry Artcile: UP TO 200,000 UCASH Industry Listing: UP TO 100,000 UCASH  IBO vs ICO  Most startups in the blockchain industry currently use a method of crowdfunding known as ICOs (Initial Coin Offerings); ICO's often lead to unfair distributions of ICOtokens, to "quick on the trigger" buyers and "whales" with large holdings of digital currencies. As a consequence, markets become manipulated giving unfair benefits to these early individuals. Regular users are therefore left out when ICOs raise millions of dollars in digital currencies within minutes, and the future0 health of the network is adversely affected.  That is why the distribution of the UCASH is using an innovative new model the Initial Bounty Offering (IBO). Users can acquire tokens by completing bounties that help build the network. Bounties range from registering an account to translating the white paper to posting on social media. IBO's help grow the network and distribute tokens efficiently and fairly. Thanks for your interest and support in the future!

Author: jm@U.CASH
Title: [ANN] - U.CASH [UCASH] Initial Bounty Offering (IBO) Now Complete!
Body: Great question! In this case you would keep your UCASH currency and gain prepaid access to U.CASH Services. Also as a Benefactor, you get to decide how your benefaction will be allocated.  A good analogy would be;  Lets say UCASH is a telecom company and we wanted to build a new cell phone network. In this case the UCASH currency would be prepaid access to our networks. Now lets say that when you purchased the prepaid access, as an added bonus, you got to decide where your benefaction can be used. In this case, lets say you cared most about a faster network you can choose to benefact network upgrades. Or... Lets say you prefer that you have access to a larger cell network, you can choose to benefact the buidling of more towers.  In this case you get to weigh in on the development of the ecosystem.  So in our case, if you believe that more users are important you can choose to benefact user sign ups, if you feel social media exposure is more effective you can choose social media bounties.  I hope i answered your question
